      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey i'm studying for my accounting exam and i'm kinda stuck on straight-line depreciation. can u give me the formula and maybe a quick example? like if i have a machine that costs 50000, has a salvage value of 5000, and lasts for 5 years, how do i do the math?",
